### [DE] contoso_itemtype
```yaml
kind: data-entity
id: contoso_itemtype
role: parameter
lifecycle: active
schema_ref: docs/dataverse-schema.md#contoso_itemtype
```
- **intent:** Parameter entity controlling how the system treats different item categories — acts as the behavioural switch for health checks, quantity limits, and categorisation
- **logic-driving fields:**
  - [DF] contoso_enablehealthcheck `boolean` — drives: [CL] HighlightHealthStatus
  - [DF] contoso_maxquantity `number` — drives: [SL] ValidateItem, [CL] EnforceQuantityLimit
  - [DF] contoso_category `choice` — Produce, Meat, Dairy, Household
- **server-logic:** (none registered on this entity)
- **client-logic:** (none on this entity's forms)
- **relationships:**
  - [DR] 1:N > [DE] contoso_shoppinglist (via: contoso_itemtypeid)
  - [DR] 1:N > [DE] contoso_listlineitem (via: contoso_itemtypeid)

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| (nothing) | — | Top-level parameter entity |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| [SL] ValidateItem | depends_on | Reads contoso_maxquantity for threshold |
| [CL] HighlightHealthStatus | depends_on | Reads contoso_enablehealthcheck flag |
| [CL] EnforceQuantityLimit | depends_on | Reads contoso_maxquantity for client-side warning |

