### [DE] contoso_shoppinglist
```yaml
kind: data-entity
id: contoso_shoppinglist
role: transactional
lifecycle: active
schema_ref: docs/dataverse-schema.md#contoso_shoppinglist
```
- **intent:** Parent record representing a specific shopping trip — aggregates line items, displays health scores, and holds computed summaries
- **logic-driving fields:**
  - [DF] contoso_nutritionscore `number` — drives: [CL] HighlightHealthStatus (trigger field)
  - [DF] contoso_totalcost `number` — drives: [CL] CalculateTotal (written by client rollup)
  - [DF] contoso_listsummary `text` — drives: [SL] ConfigurableFieldConcatenator (target field)
- **server-logic:** [SL] ConfigurableFieldConcatenator (Update.PreOperation)
- **client-logic:** [CL] HighlightHealthStatus (OnChange), [CL] CalculateTotal (OnLoad)
- **relationships:**
  - [DR] N:1 > [DE] contoso_itemtype (via: contoso_itemtypeid)
  - [DR] 1:N > [DE] contoso_listlineitem (via: contoso_shoppinglistid)

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_itemtype | depends_on | Categorisation and health check flags |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| [CL] CalculateTotal | depends_on | Rolls up from line items into this entity |
| [SL] ConfigurableFieldConcatenator | depends_on | Writes to contoso_listsummary on this entity |

---

### [DE] contoso_listlineitem
```yaml
kind: data-entity
id: contoso_listlineitem
role: transactional
lifecycle: active
schema_ref: docs/dataverse-schema.md#contoso_listlineitem
```
- **intent:** Individual item added to a shopping list — validated against inventory and quantity limits before save
- **logic-driving fields:**
  - [DF] contoso_quantity `number` — drives: [SL] ValidateItem, [SL] ConfigurableValidator, [CL] EnforceQuantityLimit
  - [DF] contoso_totalcost `number` — drives: [CL] CalculateTotal (source for parent rollup)
  - [DF] contoso_itemid `lookup` — drives: [SL] ValidateItem (resolves item type for threshold lookup)
- **server-logic:** [SL] ValidateItem (Create.PreOperation), [SL] ConfigurableValidator (Create+Update.PreOperation)
- **client-logic:** [CL] EnforceQuantityLimit (OnChange)
- **relationships:**
  - [DR] N:1 > [DE] contoso_shoppinglist (via: contoso_shoppinglistid)
  - [DR] N:1 > [DE] contoso_itemtype (via: contoso_itemtypeid)

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_shoppinglist | depends_on | Parent record |
| [DE] contoso_itemtype | depends_on | Quantity limits and categorisation |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| [CL] CalculateTotal | depends_on | Line item costs roll up to parent |
| [BP] VerifyStock | triggers | Flow triggered on line item creation |

