## 5. Server Logic [SL]

### [SL] ConfigurableFieldConcatenator
```yaml
kind: server-logic
id: configurable-field-concatenator
subtype: config-driven
lifecycle: active
```
- **intent:** Generic handler that reads field concatenation rules from config at runtime and applies them — new concat requirements are config rows, never code
- **error-behaviour:** log-and-continue (skip malformed rules, don't block save)

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_configfieldrule | depends_on | Reads all active rules for target entity at runtime |
| [SF] ConfigurationService.GetFieldRules | depends_on | Uses shared function to query config |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_shoppinglist | serves | Writes computed value to contoso_listsummary |
| [CFG] FieldConcatenation | realizes | Implements the field concatenation pattern |

**Dataverse registration:**
- Entity: contoso_shoppinglist
- Message: Update
- Stage: PreOperation
- Filtering: per config contoso_sourcefields

---

### [SL] ConfigurableValidator
```yaml
kind: server-logic
id: configurable-validator
subtype: config-driven
lifecycle: active
```
- **intent:** Generic handler that evaluates validation rules from config against record data — blocks save with user-facing error message if rule fails
- **error-behaviour:** throw (surfaces config-defined error message to user)

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_configvalidation | depends_on | Reads all active rules for target entity at runtime |
| [SF] ConfigurationService.GetValidationRules | depends_on | Uses shared function to query config |
| [SF] ConditionEvaluator.Evaluate | depends_on | Uses shared function to evaluate rule conditions |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_listlineitem | serves | Validates line item data before save |
| [CFG] Validation | realizes | Implements the validation pattern |

**Parity contract:** [CL] EnforceQuantityLimit must enforce the same quantity range rule client-side

**Dataverse registration:**
- Entity: contoso_listlineitem
- Message: Create, Update
- Stage: PreOperation
- Filtering: per config contoso_triggerfields

---

### [SL] ValidateItem
```yaml
kind: server-logic
id: validate-item
subtype: bespoke
lifecycle: active
fit_gap_ref: docs/fit-gap-analysis.md#FG-003
```
- **intent:** Checks external inventory API before save — cancels creation if item is out of stock. Bespoke because it integrates with an external system (can't be config-driven).
- **error-behaviour:** throw ("Out of stock: {itemName}")

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_itemtype | depends_on | Reads contoso_maxquantity for threshold check |
| [SF] InventoryApiClient.CheckStock | depends_on | Calls external API via shared function |
| [IB] ExternalInventoryAPI | depends_on | Underlying external system |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_listlineitem | serves | Guards line item creation |

**Dataverse registration:**
- Entity: contoso_listlineitem
- Message: Create
- Stage: PreOperation
- Filtering: contoso_itemid

---

## 6. Client Logic [CL]

### [CL] HighlightHealthStatus
```yaml
kind: client-logic
id: highlight-health-status
lifecycle: active
```
- **intent:** Visual feedback — highlights nutrition score field red when score is below threshold and health check is enabled for the item type
- **trigger:** OnChange of contoso_nutritionscore on [DE] contoso_shoppinglist form
- **writes:** contoso_nutritionscore (sets form notification)
- **parity:** [SL] ValidateNutritionScore — **TODO: not yet built**

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_itemtype | depends_on | Reads contoso_enablehealthcheck flag via API call |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| (none) | — | Terminal UI component |

**Dataverse specifics:**
- Form: MainView on contoso_shoppinglist
- Reads contoso_itemtype via `Xrm.WebApi.retrieveRecord`

---

### [CL] CalculateTotal
```yaml
kind: client-logic
id: calculate-total
lifecycle: active
```
- **intent:** Sums TotalCost from all line items and displays on the shopping list form — client-side display calculation, server uses rollup field
- **trigger:** OnLoad + Subgrid Refresh (contoso_listlineitems grid) on [DE] contoso_shoppinglist form
- **writes:** contoso_totalcost (sets value)
- **parity:** (NONE — client-only display calculation; server uses native rollup field)

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_listlineitem | depends_on | Queries line item costs via API |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| (none) | — | Terminal UI component |

**Dataverse specifics:**
- Form: MainView on contoso_shoppinglist
- Reads line items via `Xrm.WebApi.retrieveMultipleRecords`

---

### [CL] EnforceQuantityLimit
```yaml
kind: client-logic
id: enforce-quantity-limit
lifecycle: active
```
- **intent:** Client-side warning when quantity exceeds item type max — fast feedback before server-side validation catches it
- **trigger:** OnChange of contoso_quantity on [DE] contoso_listlineitem form
- **writes:** contoso_quantity (sets form notification)
- **parity:** [SL] ConfigurableValidator (range rule on contoso_quantity)

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_itemtype | depends_on | Reads contoso_maxquantity via API call |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| (none) | — | Terminal UI component |

**Dataverse specifics:**
- Form: MainView on contoso_listlineitem
- Reads contoso_itemtype via `Xrm.WebApi.retrieveRecord`

