## 9. Background Processes [BP]

### [BP] VerifyStock
```yaml
kind: background-process
id: verify-stock
lifecycle: active
```
- **intent:** Async stock verification after line item creation — non-blocking secondary check via Custom API (the synchronous check in [SL] ValidateItem is the primary gate)
- **trigger:** Record created on [DE] contoso_listlineitem

| depends_on | relationship | why |
|---|---|---|
| [DE] contoso_listlineitem | triggers | Flow triggered on line item creation |
| [API] contoso_CheckInventory | depends_on | Calls Custom API for stock verification |

| depended_on_by | relationship | impact |
|---|---|---|
| (none) | — | Terminal process; no downstream consumers |

**Dataverse specifics:**
- Type: Power Automate cloud flow
- Trigger: Dataverse connector > When a row is added (contoso_listlineitem)
- Connectors: Dataverse (Custom API call)
- Business logic: NONE — connector orchestration only per framework rules

